name: Audio Book - UI Kit
description:
Audibook is a Mobile Audio Book App UI Kit consisting of 60+ detail crafted screens that are neat, clean, modern, and easy to use.


Leverages all Figma features, including global color, font styles, dynamic components & variants. Available in Light & Dark Theme.


Fasten your work with this UI Kit, no need to start from scratch. and most importantly, it's 100% completely free!
